Package animation

Class Summary
AnimationState A container holding information for help displaying a situation on the view.
AnimationStateQueue A complex data structure for helping the animator to queue animation states, so that the states can be allocated to the turns they were created in.
Animator Connects view and model by observing the model and creating information for representation on the gui.
